assets.description: In Malaysia, there are 3 islands known to host all 7 types of turtles nesting worldwide.  Reef Balls were used on the main island to successfully protect turtle nesting beach which was eroding away.  A very large sized Reef ball (Golieth with lifter rings) where used due to a very high tidal range.  This is a 3-d map used for planning the deployment.
